  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Dad asked me to come along on his Saturday errands downtown, promising it would only take an hour, which turned out to be completely wrong.",
      "zh": "爸爸請我星期六陪他去市區辦事，保證只要一小時，結果完全不是這麼回事。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Our first stop was the supermarket, where he checked his paper map of the store because he could never remember which aisle sold cooking oil.",
      "zh": "我們第一站是超市，爸爸查了一張店內地圖，因為他永遠記不住煮菜用的油放在哪一排。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Next, we walked along a busy sidewalk near the old city gate, where a stone soldier statue has stood guard for over a hundred years.",
      "zh": "接著我們沿著舊城門附近一條繁忙的人行道走，那裡有一座石頭士兵雕像已經站崗超過一百年了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Dad pointed out that the building behind the gate used to be an old prison, though today it is just an empty government office.",
      "zh": "爸爸指出城門後面那棟建築物以前曾經是一座監獄，不過現在只是一間空蕩蕩的政府辦公室。"
    },
    {
      "en": "We stopped at a small jewelry shop so Dad could pick up Mom's ring, which had been sent there for a small repair.",
      "zh": "我們在一間小小的珠寶店停下來，爸爸要去取媽媽送修的戒指。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The shopkeeper, a polite lady, called Dad \"sir\" the entire time and handed him a small key to a locked display case.",
      "zh": "店主是位很有禮貌的女士，全程稱呼爸爸「先生」，還遞給他一把小小的展示櫃鑰匙。"
    },
    {
      "en": "After that, we needed to find a restroom, and Dad finally spotted a public toilet near a hotel lobby just off the main street.",
      "zh": "之後我們需要找洗手間，爸爸終於在主要街道旁一間飯店大廳附近找到一間公共廁所。"
    },
    {
      "en": "We passed a small park near the sea, where a few visitors watched a large ship slowly leaving the shore in the distance.",
      "zh": "我們經過海邊一座小公園，幾位遊客正看著一艘大船緩緩離開遠處的岸邊。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Dad said he used to dream of buying land near the coast someday, though right now that dream mostly lives inside his own head.",
      "zh": "爸爸說他以前夢想有一天能在海岸附近買一塊地，不過現在這個夢大概只存在他自己的腦袋裡。"
    },
    {
      "en": "At lunch, we sat at a small restaurant, and Dad left a generous tip because the waiter had been friendly the entire meal.",
      "zh": "午餐時我們坐在一間小餐廳，爸爸留了一筆大方的小費，因為服務生整頓飯都很親切。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The owner shook Dad's hand warmly and said \"welcome back\" as we were leaving, since apparently Dad eats there more often than I realized.",
      "zh": "老闆熱情地跟爸爸握手，我們離開時說了句「歡迎再來」，看來爸爸來這裡吃飯的次數比我以為的還多。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the time we finally got home, my feet hurt, my bag was full of small errands, and Dad's \"one quick hour\" had turned into an entire afternoon.",
      "zh": "我們終於到家的時候，我的腳很痠、袋子裡裝滿了各種瑣事，爸爸口中「快速的一小時」已經變成了一整個下午。"
    }
  ],
